# Stage-0 experiment scratch — keep the repo clean of huge external clones, models, venvs, audio.
# cloned external tools (ACE-Step-1.5, Smule-Renaissance-Small) — each has its own .git.
# NOTE: inline comments (after a pattern on the same line) break .gitignore matching —
# git treats them as part of the pattern, so `vendor/` was NOT actually ignored (17 GB leaked
# into `git status`). Keep comments on their OWN lines.
vendor/
# tool caches (acestep, etc.)
.cache/
.venv*/
__pycache__/
*.pyc
models/
out/
data/*
!data/README.md
*.wav
*.flac
*.mp3
*.m4a
*.safetensors
*.ckpt
*.pt
*.pth
